Package: playit
Version: 0.17.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, rust, build-essential, pkg-config
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://playit.gg/
Description: Global Proxy for Server Hosting Without Port Forwarding
 Playit is a global proxy service that allows anyone to host servers
 without port forwarding. Creates secure tunnels to expose local
 services to the internet with automatic SSL and global accessibility.
 Supports TCP, UDP, and HTTP traffic.
